{
 "file": "_STGSP5B.bin",
 "source_size": 36984,
 "built_size": 38945,
 "edits": [
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x14be",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "米莉亚莉亚！先锋母舰那边、有联络过{00}来吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e878e81ee7d6e81ee7d606b8e967e9d5e7d4e7b7e89902e7cbef2eeb14ef3600d9e80206050000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x14ec",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不行！通信被完全切断了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5efd6ef97ef59e90fe7f1e87eefb4ef3fe982e7ba09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x151f",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……我方的指挥官、全都被扣作人质了{00}吗……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909efccefb1e7b4e8c0e949ef9202efb4e840e7f1ee2aef2fefb2eb45e7ba00e8020909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1563",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……就趁现在、贝拉舰长！让先锋母舰{00}后撤！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c5e9eae82fef2902e857e7c2e7d4ef3406e7f9b8e967e9d5e7d400e7fee90a06060000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x158e",
   "jp_len": 1,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "ec"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x158f",
   "jp_len": 56,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "153302000206c00013741733020001065800131c1633020001064b0006580013f5163302000215e81d0909e7e3efb1e7b4ef28efb0e7f7ef29e7b5e982ea3de85402e7b9e7daef4d00e7ebe7c4e7b5ecc70909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15e2",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "振作起来、贝拉·罗纳！！{00}快让舰艇后撤啊！",
   "zh_hex": "15eb5bef2fe847d902e857e7c204e7ece882060600e85fe7f9e7d4eb6be7fee90ae7c30600000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1624",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c309090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x162a",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "先、先锋母舰……全速后撤……",
   "zh_hex": "15b802b8e967e9d5e7d40909bbe9dae7fee90a090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x165e",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "您没事吧、玛琉！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e835e7d8efb8e7d002e845ead2ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x168d",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我这边没事！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b9e899e7d8efb8ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1696",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "只是……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef32e7b609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16d8",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "早知道……早知道会变成这样……",
   "zh_hex": "15e963e85ae82a0909e963e85ae82ae7e2e955e837e7b9e7da09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16eb",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我……当初什么都不做就好了……",
   "zh_hex": "15efcc0909ef53eb4fe7dde7bde840e7b5e81ce7c5e7c7e7ba09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x171c",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "贝拉！请您振作起来啊！",
   "zh_hex": "15e857e7c2ef97e83ae835eb5bef2fe847efcfe7c3ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x172d",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你要是这副样子……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8ef2ae7b6e7b9ecb6e7dae88609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x175f",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "木星帝国军、已经开始进攻了！",
   "zh_hex": "15efa9ef69e8f8efc4e7e002ef3ae8b7e7fae908e892ef67e7baef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1796",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "贝拉舰长既然是那副样子、迎击只能交给{00}其余三艘舰来打了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e857e7c2e7d4ef34e8c4e7efe7b6e7b7ecb6e7dae88602e931e7ccef32e7c6e861e83900e8cfeb27eaa0eb18e7d4d9e7f5e7ba0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17e7",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "都怪我挑起了这场战争、他才会……",
   "zh_hex": "15e840ea07efcceae7e847e7bae7b9e876ef28e85202e80ce836e7e209090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17ff",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "金凯度他……",
   "zh_hex": "15e902e95fe96de80c09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x182c",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那个人、是拼上性命、想要守护您和这艘{00}舰的、不是吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e828efb202e7b6ea66ef4ce951e85302e7e6ef2ae8a8e8e0e835e7d3e7b9eb1800e7d4e7b402e7b5e7b6e802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1878",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "拉克丝……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c2e7d5e8a30909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x189d",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "既然如此、您就必须回应他这份心意才行",
   "zh_hex": "15e8c4e7efe7f0e7ca02e835e7c5e860e9a2ef52e873e80ce7b9ea22e82def3ce836efd60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18e1",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我来……",
   "zh_hex": "15efccefcf09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x190d",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "一味沉浸在悲伤之中、{00}是不会有任何结果的",
   "zh_hex": "1587ed36e983ee52ef29e9dfe8f9e7cdc00200e7b6e7b5e7e2e7cbe89a8ae868e871e7b40000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1926",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "如果您心里仍然在意着他、就更应该去回{00}应他的意志",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f0e871e835e82def31eab9e7efef29ef3ce86de80c02e7c5e952e873e898e7ebef5200e873e80ce7b4ef3cea180000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x196f",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我……",
   "zh_hex": "15efcc09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1993",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我来做！我来！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efccefcfe81cef97efccefcfef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19c3",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……舰长！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7d4ef34ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19e6",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好！我们也跟在先锋母舰后面冲上去！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c7068be7bbe7c0e973ef29b8e967e9d5e7d4e7fee862e95eb2e7eb06000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19fa",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "预防者全队、立刻开始攻击！向木星帝国{00}军发起反击！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ea5ae968ef6eefb4e7c902e86be91fe7fae908ef67e7ccef97efc1efa9ef69e8f8efc400e7e0e870e847e87ce7ccef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a3e",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "敌部队的反应、消失了！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e3ef70e7c9e7b4e87ce87302e928e8a5e7baef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a68",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呼……总之、总算是勉强撑过去了",
   "zh_hex": "15ea3c0909e881e7cd02e881e889e7b6eb2ae8adea29ef36e7ebe7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a7d",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "接下来就剩……",
   "zh_hex": "15efceef4defcfe7c5ea3a09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1aaa",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……请不必担心我",
   "zh_hex": "150909e83ae7b5e860e9fde82d8b00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ad8",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "贝拉舰长……您也别太勉强自己了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e857e7c2e7d4ef340909e835e7c0e7e5e86aeb2ae8adefb5e8c9e7ba09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b13",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b37",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是、是木星帝国军！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b602e7b6efa9ef69e8f8efc4e7e0ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b69",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔、不妙……我们这边、可才刚结束一场{00}战斗啊！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d02e7b5ecc70909efcce7bbe7b9e89902e7c4e836e8bce868e895efb6e87600ef28e7ffe7c3ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1baa",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "刚才那场战斗的结果、我已整理成报告、{00}传回本部了",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bce836e7b7e876ef28e7ffe7b4e868e87102efccef3ae9fee872e837e913e8e50200ea38ef52efa6ef70e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1be4",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "辛苦你了……米莉亚莉亚",
   "zh_hex": "15ea58e9e6e7b8e7ba0909e878e81ee7d6e81ee7d60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c0c",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好了……接下来、就看上层愿不愿意相信{00}我们了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c7e7ba0909efceef4defcf02e7c5e7f6ef4cebc1e961e7b5e961ef3ce8b1e90f00efcce7bbe7ba09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c44",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "他们要是不肯相信、那可就麻烦了",
   "zh_hex": "15e80ce7bbef2ae7b6e7b5e93de8b1e90f02e7b7e7c4e7c5ea36e95be7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c54",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "想要阻挡木星帝国、单凭我们的力量、是{00}远远不够的",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e6ef2ae8efea77d4b5e8f8a102e918ea498be7bbe7b4dae85102e7b600e94ce94ce7b5e920e7b400000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c8c",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "竟然已经把那么庞大的战力、送进了地球{00}圈……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ce7efef3ae8b7e81be7b7e7bded55efa5e7b4ef28efb002e9bae892e7baef63efd300e9fb09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1cc4",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "他们进攻地球的作战、恐怕已经到了最后{00}阶段了吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e80ce7bbe892ef67ef63efd3e7b4ef2fef2802eb33e958ef3ae8b7e7d7e7bae8c5e7fe00ebfbea6be7bae7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1cfe",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "贝拉舰长？",
   "zh_hex": "15e857e7c2e7d4ef34050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d06",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你……真没事吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b80909e820e7d8efb8e802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d32",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……请别担心、失去他、确实是沉重的打{00}击……",
   "zh_hex": "150909e83ae7e5e9fde82d02e8a5e7ebe80c02e88ce87fe7b6e983e8a1e7b4e7f500e7cc09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d4f",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可我们不能就此停下",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4efcce7bbe7b5e7c6e7c5e7cae934ef4d0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d83",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嗯……",
   "zh_hex": "15e86509090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1da5",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "比起这个、拉米亚斯舰长",
   "zh_hex": "15e825e847e7b9e82802e7c2e878e7d6e7c8e7d4ef340000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1db1",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们眼下应该做的、是如何应对木星帝国",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe90bef4de873e898e81ce7b402e7b6e7f0efbce873e7beefa9ef69e8f8efc40000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1de7",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "军本部那边、怎么说？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e0efa6ef70e7b7e89902e7f2e7bde7ed050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e0f",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……算是半信半疑",
   "zh_hex": "150909e889e7b6eadee90feadeeb62000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e22",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "因为上面要求我们返航、{00}与正规军会合……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef33e7c1b2e862ef2ae93a8be7bbeba8e9c10200e832ef3bea42e7e0e7e2a009090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e42",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "看来他们、多少还是有些危机感……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f6efcfe80ce7bb02e7e9eface7f7e7b6e7cbe8a4e935e7e4e87d09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e79",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……木星帝国的进攻、可以认为很快就要{00}开始了",
   "zh_hex": "150909efa9ef69e8f8efc4e7b4e892ef6702e7c4e7f3e8a0e7c1e981e85fe7c5ef2a00e7fae908e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e98",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "现在必须争分夺秒地整备战力、加固对他{00}们的防备",
   "zh_hex": "15e82fef29e860e9a2e852efaeea17ee79ef63e9fee877ef28efb002e854eac0e7bee80c00e7bbe7b4e968e8770000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ed6",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……说得对、{00}那就先抓紧时间、返回本部吧",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7ede80ae7be0200e7b7e7c5b8e962eaedef2de8fc02eba88cd2cce7d0000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f0c",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "各舰的修理情况如何？",
   "zh_hex": "15e819e7d4e7b4e9b0e872e88be8d0e7f0efbc050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f33",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "预计马上就能完成",
   "zh_hex": "15ea5aea55e84fef4ce7c5e7c6e87ee8370000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f5e",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、待修理完成、{00}预防者全员返回本部！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02eaa8e9b0e872e87ee8370200ea5ae968adbbe849eba88cd2cc060000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f79",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "与正规军会合、做好迎击木星帝国进攻的{00}准备！",
   "zh_hex": "15e832ef3bea42e7e0e7e2efc002e81ce7c7e931e7ccefa9ef69e8f8efc4e892ef67e7b400e87ae877ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x69e2",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "竟、竟然就到此为止了……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2c02ef2ce7efe7c5e7d7e7cae7c1e869e7ba09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6b9e",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呵呵呵……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3def3def3d09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6bce",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你就是十字先锋的扎比涅·夏尔吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7c5e7b6ea4ae980b8e967e7b4e84be825eacf04ef37e7e1e7d00500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6be2",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……联络、我已经收到了",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef2eeb1402efccef3ae8b7e926e7d7e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6c22",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、投降的条件也……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e948e943e7b4e9d4e991e7c009090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6c55",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我会保证你、以及贝拉·罗纳舰长的安全",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7e2ea47eba3e7b802e7f3e9cfe857e7c2ef4be7ece882e7d4ef34e7b4e7fcefb40000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6c86",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……对了、你们最好别轻举妄动",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7bee7ba02e7b8e7bbe8c5e7c7e7e5e990ea21ecc6ef300000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6c98",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "先锋母舰的主炮、可正对准着你们呢",
   "zh_hex": "15b8e967e9d5e7d4e7b4e954e95a02e7c4ef3be7bee87ae86de7b8e7bbe9070000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6cb0",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "敢动、呵呵……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8cdef3002ef3def3d0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6ce6",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81def97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6d23",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "扎比涅！你这家伙！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e84be825eacf06e7b8e7b9e7dfe7fd06060000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6d44",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啧！是金凯度吗！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e9faef97e7b6e902e95fe96de802ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6d76",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可恶！是海盗的同伙吗！！全员、进入战{00}斗配置……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7deef97e7b6e91be9f3e7b4e85de7fde802ef97ef97efb4e84902e892e891ef2800e7ffea34ea0e09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6dc4",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……等等！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e826e826ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6df2",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81def97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6e2a",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "放走他、是我的疏忽……那就由我负责、{00}亲手了结他",
   "zh_hex": "15e86ce890e80c02e7b68be7b4ee6eed770909e7b7e7c5e8a68be92ceba60200e894aee7bae868e80c0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6e6b",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……好、好吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909e7c702e7c7e7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6e9e",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……就是这么回事、金凯度",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c5e7b6e7b9e7bdef52efb802e902e95fe96d0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6eac",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我不想让旁人插手、和你单独做个了断、{00}嘿嘿……",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b5e7e6e7f9ef04efb2eb08ef6602e7d3e7b8e918e8eee81ce828e7bae9820200e85ee85e09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6efc",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "扎比涅、你想干什么？",
   "zh_hex": "15e84be825eacf02e7b8e7e6e8d3e7dde7bd050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6f2a",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……来吧、放马过来、金凯度",
   "zh_hex": "150909efcfe7d002e86ce84fef36efcf02e902e95fe96d0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6f39",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你若能打倒我、我答应放了贝拉大人、又{00}何妨？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7e7e7c6e7f5e848efcc02efccea96e873e86ce7bae857e7c2efa5efb202e8f100efbce97f050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6f59",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哈、哈哈、哈！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e802e7e8e7e802e7e8ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6f97",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啧、扎比涅……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e9fa02e84be825eacf090906000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6fd7",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……好吧",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c7e7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6fe1",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你的算计……我就奉陪到底！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b4e889ea550909efcce7c5eac1ef42e7d7e9b4ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7008",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哈、哈哈哈！！这才像样、金凯度！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e802e7e8e7e8e7e8ef97ef97e7b9e836e8e9e7da02e902e95fe96def97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x703a",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呵呵呵、我就知道你会上当",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3def3def3d028be7c5e85ae82ae7b8e7e2b2c40000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x70ad",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "毕竟、你和我之间……",
   "zh_hex": "15ea2cef2c02e7b8e7d3efcce7cde8fc09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x70bc",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "看来、你我之间、本就注定要决一死战啊！{00}金凯度——！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f6d902e7b88be7cde8fc02d2e7c5eacce867ef2ae8ab87a7ef28e7c30600e902e95fe96debafebaf060600000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7113",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "打倒你、把贝拉救出来……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f5e848e7b802e81be857e7c2e8caefbeefcf09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7125",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……做好觉悟吧！扎比涅——！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e81ce7c7e8aeea19e7d006e84be825eacfebafebaf06060000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x715e",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……啧！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e9faef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x718e",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "到此为止了！扎比涅！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d7e7cae7c1e869e7ba06e84be825eacf06060000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x71c2",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嘿嘿嘿嘿！当真如此吗、金凯度——！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e85ee85ee85ee85eef97ef53e820e7f0e7cae80202e902e95fe96debafebafef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7202",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么、你这家伙！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bd02e7b8e7b9e7dfe7fdef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7226",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可恶！竟没能给他致命一击吗！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7deef97ef2ce7d8e7c6e839e80cea32e853efb6e7cce802ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x726e",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "金凯度……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e902e95fe96d0909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7280",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "只要、只要没有你这个人……！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef32ef2a02ef32ef2ae7d8e7cbe7b8e7b9e828efb20909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x729e",
   "jp_len": 40,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "贝拉大人若不是对你动了心、又怎会舍弃{00}贵族主义！",
   "zh_hex": "15e857e7c2efa5efb2e7e7e7b5e7b6e7bee7b8ef30e7bae82d02e8f1e7f2e7e2eb17e93800e930eb5ee954e8ceef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x72f6",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "拿命来赎罪吧！！金凯度！",
   "zh_hex": "15e9a7e853efcfeff1ea7fe7d0ef97ef97e902e95fe96def970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x733a",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "糟了！？",
   "zh_hex": "15eeafe7ba06050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7372",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "金凯度！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e902e95fe96def97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x739e",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "贝、贝拉……对不起……",
   "zh_hex": "15e85702e857e7c20909e7bee7b5e84709090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x73da",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊哈哈哈！啊哈哈哈哈哈！！{00}永别了！金凯度！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c3e7e8e7e8e7e806e7c3e7e8e7e8e7e8e7e8e7e8060600e9bfe7e5e7ba06e902e95fe96d0600000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7422",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "金凯度——！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e902e95fe96debafebafef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x745b",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可恶！金凯度先生他！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7deef97e902e95fe96def8bef8de80cef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7492",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "托比亚……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f4e825e7d6090906000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x74c2",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "先锋母舰被夺、这下连金凯度先生也…{00}…！",
   "zh_hex": "15b8e967e9d5e7d4e7f1ea1702e7b989e86ee902e95fe96db8b6e7c009000906000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x74da",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……可恶！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c4e7deef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7519",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊、托比亚！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c302e7f4e825e7d60605000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x755e",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……是托比亚吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909e7b6e7f4e825e7d6e8020605000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7584",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你们这帮家伙……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7bbe7b9e910e7dfe7fd0909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7599",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "别给我开这种玩笑啊——！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e5e839efcce7fae7b9e7d1e970ea1ce7c3ebafebafef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x75d6",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啧！是海盗！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e9faef97e7b6e91be9f3ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x760a",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "先锋母舰！全舰、转入攻击态势！！",
   "zh_hex": "15b8e967e9d5e7d406bbe7d402e9c2e8919ee7cce994e8fd060600000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x761b",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "把木星帝国军、彻底击破！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81befa9ef69e8f8efc4e7e002ebc5e9b4e7ccef6def97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7652",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "全舰、准备攻击！",
   "zh_hex": "15efb4e7d402e87ae877ef67e7ccef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x765d",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "向违抗杜加奇总统的海盗们、降下制裁的{00}铁锤吧！",
   "zh_hex": "159deab2e912e8cbe854e904e881e929e7b4e91be9f3e7bb02e94389e8deec39e7b400eebbedc2e7d0060000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x76a2",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "等等！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e826e826ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x76d2",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "贝尔纳黛特！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e857e7e1e882ea9ae7cfef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7702",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不许你们、对这些人动手！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5e8a7e7b8e7bb02e7bee7b9e8a4efb2ef30ef66ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7734",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什、什么、你是谁！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dd02e7dde7bd02e7b8e7b6e923ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x775d",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我、是提提妮斯·杜加奇",
   "zh_hex": "158b02e7b6e821e821ebbce7c804e8cbe854e90400000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7767",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是格拉克斯·杜加奇总统的女儿",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e824e7c2e7d5e7c804e8cbe854e904e881e929e7b4b0eb7c00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7791",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎、怎么会……贝尔纳黛特？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f202e7f2e7bde7e20909e857e7e1e882ea9ae7cf050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x77ba",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那孩子、竟是杜加奇的……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e956e88602ef2ce7b6e8cbe854e904e7b40909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x77ee",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "司、司令……那张脸、的确是提提妮斯大{00}人的……",
   "zh_hex": "15eafe02eafee94e0909e7b7eac5eb6902e7b4e88ce7b6e821e821ebbce7c8efa500efb2e7b409090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7823",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔、唔唔……",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d02e81de81d09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7856",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "父亲杜加奇、此刻一定正在四处找我……",
   "zh_hex": "15e888e894e8cbe854e90402e7cae91f87e867ef3bef29eb52e903e9d28b090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x786f",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "只要你们肯放过他们、我就跟你们一起、{00}回到父亲身边",
   "zh_hex": "15ef32ef2ae7b8e7bbe93de86cef36e80ce7bb02efcce7c5e973e7b8e7bbefb6e8470200ef52e7d7e888e894e88de8990000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x78ae",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那……是真的吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b70909e7b6e820e7b4e802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x78d5",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "身为总统的女儿、我绝不食言",
   "zh_hex": "15e88de7c1e881e929e7b4efadeb7c02efcce91ce7b5edc9efd70000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x790c",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那好吧",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7c7e7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7918",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、作为接您回去的交换、就放过那些{00}人吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02ef2fe7c1efcee835ef52e7ebe7b4e861ea7802e7c5e86cef36e7b7e8a400efb2e7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x795e",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……司令！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909eafee94eef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7982",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "无妨！提提妮斯大人的安危才是首要！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dce97fef97e821e821ebbce7c8efa5efb2e7b4e7fce935e836e7b6ef40ef2aef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x79b5",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7b609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x79d7",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "终归是支垂死的部队、放着不管、也成不{00}了什么气候",
   "zh_hex": "15e8e2e947e7b6e883ed41ef6ae7b4ef70e7c902e86ce86de7b5e93b02e7c0e837e7b500e7bae7dde7bde8edea390000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x79f7",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "再说、就算我们不特意出手、反正他们也{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15e80be7ed02e7c5e889efcce7bbe7b5e7cfef3cefbeef6602e87cef3be80ce7bbe7c00009090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7a53",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "快、护送提提妮斯大人回去！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e85f02e8e0e9bae821e821ebbce7c8efa5efb2ef52e7ebef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7a8a",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……贝尔纳黛特！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e857e7e1e882ea9ae7cfef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7ab0",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "别担心、托比亚",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e5e9fde82d02e7f4e825e7d60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7abc",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我、会去见父亲大人、试着说服他停止这{00}场战争",
   "zh_hex": "15efcc02e7e2e7ebe85ce888e894efa5efb202e91de86de7ede9f1e80ce934e869e7b900e876ef28e8520000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7af5",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "请吧……提提妮斯大人",
   "zh_hex": "15e83ae7d00909e821e821ebbce7c8efa5efb20000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7b1a",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7b46",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可恶……贝尔纳黛特！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7de0909e857e7e1e882ea9ae7cfef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7b9e",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……贝拉",
   "zh_hex": "150909e857e7c20000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7bc2",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊……托比亚？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c30909e7f4e825e7d6050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7be6",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那个……金凯度先生的事……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e8280909e902e95fe96def8bef8de7b4efb809090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7c10",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你在为我担心吗？谢谢你、托比亚",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8ef29e7c18be9fde82de80205e8b2e8b2e7b802e7f4e825e7d6000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7c23",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过、我没事的",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef3602efcce7d8efb8e7b40000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7c34",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你也一直担心着她、我也不能光顾着伤心{00}啊",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7c0efb6e875e9fde82de86de88e02efcce7c0e7b5e7c6e83dea1fe86de8f9e82d00e7c30000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7c74",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "金、金凯度先生他！金凯度先生他还没有{00}死！",
   "zh_hex": "15e90202e902e95fe96def8bef8de80cef97e902e95fe96def8bef8de80ce7f7e7d8e7cb00ef6aef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7c8e",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就凭那点事、他怎么可能会死啊！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5ea49e7b7e822efb802e80ce7f2e7bde7c4e7c6e7e2ef6ae7c3ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7cc5",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……没关系的、托比亚",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7d8e8bbe941e7b402e7f4e825e7d60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7cd1",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "人啊、不管怎样、该走的时候……终究还{00}是会走的",
   "zh_hex": "15efb2e7c302e7b5e93be7f2e7da02e898e890e7b4ef2dea390909e8e2e906e7f700e7b6e7e2e890e7b40000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7d2a",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "从前啊……",
   "zh_hex": "15e88aef51e7c309090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7d4d",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "贝拉……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e857e7c20909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7d72",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在我下定决心要与木星帝国一战的那一天{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29efccef4de867e8abe82def2ae832efa9ef69e8f8efc4efb6ef28e7b4e7b7efb6e8440009090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7d8c",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那个人、舍弃了过去的名字、选择以金凯{00}度自称",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e828efb202eb17e938e7baef36e7ebe7b4e8ace98002e966eaaae7f3e902e95f00e96defb5ea010000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7dc5",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "过去的名字……他舍弃了西布克·阿诺这{00}个名字……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef36e7ebe7b4e8ace9800909e80ceb17e938e7bae7f8e831e7d5ef4be7d2e972e7b900e828e8ace98009090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7dfb",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……嗯",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8650000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7e02",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我不明白那究竟是为什么、就算去问他、{00}他也始终不肯回答",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b5ef39e809e7b7e906ef2ce7b6e7c1e7dde7bd02e7c5e889e7ebe997e80c0200e80ce7c0e908e8e2e7b5e93def52ea960000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7e24",
   "jp_len": 40,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "因为他总是陪在我身边……我便自以为、{00}彼此的心意早已相通",
   "zh_hex": "15ef33e7c1e80ce881e7b6ef42ef29efcce88de8990909efcce8faefb5e7f3e7c10200efc9e7cae7b4e82def3ce963ef3ae8b1ef590000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7e4c",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "所以、我没有再追问下去",
   "zh_hex": "15e7fbe7f3028be7d8e7cbe80be8dde99789e7eb000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7e5f",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "但也许从那时起……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dbe7c0e8a7e88ae7b7ef2de84709090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7e72",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "也许、我并没有像自己以为的那样、真正{00}读懂他的心",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c0e8a702efcce957e7d8e7cbe8e9efb5e8c9e7f3e7c1e7b4e7b7e7da02e820ef3b00eea0e8b0e80ce7b4e82d0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7eb1",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是这样吗",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6e7b9e7dae8020000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7ed8",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "咦……？",
   "zh_hex": "15ef490909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7efa",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "贝拉以前、不也叫塞西莉·菲亚查德吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e857e7c2e7f3ef5102e7b5e7c0e8c1e950e7f8e81eef4bea6ce7d6eae9e82ce802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7f38",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嗯、嗯……那是为了躲开身为贵族主义者{00}的祖父……",
   "zh_hex": "15e86502e8650909e7b7e7b6e7c1e7baea6fe7fae88de7c1e930eb5ee954e8ceef6e00e7b4ebe1e88809090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7f73",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可是、金凯度先生……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7b602e902e95fe96def8bef8d09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7f7f",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不、对西布克·阿诺来说、那才是他真正{00}的名字",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b502e7bee7f8e831e7d5ef4be7d2e972efcfe7ed02e7b7e836e7b6e80ce820ef3b00e7b4e8ace9800000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7fb5",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我的、真名……",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b402e820e8ac09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7fdd",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "金凯度·纳乌这个名字、",
   "zh_hex": "15e902e95fe96def4be882e94de7b9e828e8ace980020000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7fec",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是为了陪伴想要再次扮演贝拉·罗纳的{00}你、才必须用上的",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e7c1e7baef42ea72e7e6ef2ae80be864ec70ea2fe857e7c204e7ece882e7b400e7b802e836e860e9a2d8b2e7b40000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x800d",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是他所扮演角色的名字……我有这样的{00}感觉",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6e80ce7fbec70ea2feb1ae89fe7b4e8ace98009098be7cbe7b9e7dae7b400e87de8ae000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x806c",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……啊、我说话太放肆了、真对不起",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c302efcce7ede81fe86ae86cedaae7ba02e820e7bee7b5e8470000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x809e",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不……谢谢你、托比亚",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b50909e8b2e8b2e7b802e7f4e825e7d60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x80f9",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "（金凯度先生……他之所以需要一个扮演{00}的名字……）",
   "zh_hex": "15ef8ee902e95fe96def8bef8d0909e80ce7cde7fbe7f3e92def2aefb6e828ec70ea2f00e7b4e8ace9800909ef8f0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8115",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "（不正是为了、在战斗结束之后、变回真{00}正的两个人吗？）",
   "zh_hex": "15ef8ee7b5ef3be7b6e7c1e7ba02ef29ef28e7ffe868e895e7cde7fe02e955ef52e82000ef3be7b4e97de828efb2e80205ef8f0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8138",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "（可是、一切都还没有结束）",
   "zh_hex": "15ef8ee7c4e7b602efb6ef3fe840e7f7e7d8e7cbe868e895ef8f0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x814c",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "（所以、金凯度先生……）",
   "zh_hex": "15ef8ee7fbe7f302e902e95fe96def8bef8d0909ef8f0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x815a",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "（你、是一定要回来的）",
   "zh_hex": "15ef8ee7b802e7b6efb6e867ef2aef52efcfe7b4ef8f0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x816e",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "（回到这里……回到贝拉身边……）",
   "zh_hex": "15ef8eef52e7d7e7b9ef310909ef52e7d7e857e7c2e88de8990909ef8f0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x819e",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你回来了……提提妮斯",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8ef52efcfe7ba0909e821e821ebbce7c80000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x81c7",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "父、父亲大人……",
   "zh_hex": "15e88802e888e894efa5efb209090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x81ee",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "久违的父女相见、就让我听听、你想说些{00}什么吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e9dbeab2e7b4e888efade8b1e85c02e7c5e7f9efcce8d1e8d102e7b8e7e6e7ede8a400e7dde7bde7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8211",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "提提妮斯、你想向我杜加奇求取什么？是{00}自由吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e821e821ebbce7c802e7b8e7e69d8be8cbe854e904e93ae987e7dde7bd05e7b600abe8a6e802050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8241",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我、我希望您、能停止对地球的进攻……",
   "zh_hex": "15efcc02efcce87be965e83502e7c6e934e869e7beef63efd3e7b4e892ef6709090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8279",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哦？",
   "zh_hex": "15e919050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x829a",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "即便那是为了、给木星的人民、带来一片{00}富饶的土地……",
   "zh_hex": "15e855e8fae7b7e7b6e7c1e7ba02e839d4b5e7b4b4ef3802e937d987ee5e00ec8feab5e7b4ec56bf09090000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x82c0",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我、我也绝不认为、那是正确的事！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcc02efcce7c0e91ce7b5e8a0e7c102e7b7e7b6ef3be88ce7b4efb8ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x82dc",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "所以、父亲大人……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7fbe7f302e888e894efa5efb209090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8304",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呵……呵……！哈哈哈哈哈哈！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3d0909ef3d0909ef97e7e8e7e8e7e8e7e8e7e8e7e8ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8318",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "进攻地球！你说进攻地球！？真是笑死人{00}了！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e892ef67ef63efd3ef97e7b8e7ede892ef67ef63efd3ef9705e820e7b6ea1cef6aefb200e7baef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8350",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "父、父亲大人……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e88802e888e894efa5efb20909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8378",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "提提妮斯、你此刻呼吸着的这空气、是什{00}么？",
   "zh_hex": "15e821e821ebbce7c802e7b8e7cae91fea3ced34e86de7b4e7b9e93fe8ed02e7b6e7dd00e7bd050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x83aa",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……诶？",
   "zh_hex": "150909eaf3050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x83cc",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你平时喝的那些水、又是从哪来的！给我{00}好好想想！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e887ef2dec54e7b4e7b7e8a4ebd402e8f1e7b6e88ae8ffefcfe7b4ef97e839efcc00e7c7e7c7e7e6e7e6ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8430",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么都没有！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bde840e7d8e7cbef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x843b",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在木星上！根本没有任何、从地球带来的{00}东西！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29efa9ef69ef4cef97e9b8efa6e7d8e7cbe89aefbc02e88aef63efd3e937efcfe7b400e8bae7f8ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8454",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "没错……一切、都能靠人工来供给！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d8e8850909efb6ef3f02e840e7c6e8c7efb2eae4efcfeca9e839ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x846a",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8472",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就算把地球弄到手、又能有多大的意义？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5e889e81bef63efd3eac4e7d7ef6602e8f1e7c6e7cbe7e9efa5e7b4ef3ce8ce050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x84a5",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "父、父亲大人……{00}您到底、想做什么……？",
